snippet.title: Awesome CNC Freak
snippet.description:
Let's Enjoy making awesome things with the CNC machine at home !
I had a dream of having my own CNC machine and making what I like. 
One day, I realized that the era was reached that it is possible to make my own CNC machine, and I made an amazing 5 axis CNC machine in 3 years.
I want to say that Thanks to LinuxCNC, Fuson360 and popularization of 3D printers.
The time has come! Subscribe to this channel and Let's enjoy metalwork with drinking beer together.
